 remain at ",["STRONG",{},"£42"]," per brown bin."]]],["HR"],["P",{},["STRONG",{},"Would you like to know what happens to the contents of your bins once they have been collected?"]," Then please take a look at ",["A",{"href":"/wheredoesitgo"},"Where Does it Go"],", which shows the destinations of the recycling and waste collected in Stafford Borough."],["P",{},"You can check your collection dates online ",["A",{"href":"https://www.staffordbc.gov.uk/about-my-area"},"www.staffordbc.gov.uk/collectiondays"],"."],["P",{},"Your wheeled bins must be ready by 7am on collection day and placed at your nearest collection point at the boundary of your property. Please ensure your bin is clearly visible for the collection crew and not causing inconvenience to others."],["P",{},"We provide one bin per household for each service you receive. Please see below for further information."],["UL",{},["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-additional-larger-or-smaller-bins","title":"Additional, larger or smaller bins"},"Additional, Larger or Smaller Bins"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-assisted-collection-service","title":"Assisted collections"},"Assisted Collections"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/badweather","title":"Bin collections in severe weather"},"Bin Collections in Severe Weather"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-civic-amenity-site-visits","title":"Civic Amenity Site visits"},"Civic Amenity Site Visits"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-what-do-i-do-if","title":"Recycling and Waste frequently asked questions"},"Frequently Asked Questions"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-furniture-re-use-projects","title":"Furniture re-use projects"},"Furniture re-use Projects"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-household-waste-recycling-centre-tip","title":"Household recycling centres (Tip)"},"Household Waste Recycling Centre"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/recycling-and-waste-know-your-bins","title":"What goes in which bin"},"Know Your 